Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [14.08.2025]

This Privacy Policy describes how your information is handled when you use the mobile game [Your Game Name] ("the Game").

1. Information We Collect

The Game itself does not collect, store, or share any personal information from its users.

2. Web Content

The Game contains a single in-app WebView that loads an HTML game hosted on GitHub Pages.
The WebView is restricted to opening only one specific webpage:
https://tolstiapps.github.io/jumping-cat/
No other websites can be accessed from within the Game.

3. Third-Party Services

The Game does not use analytics, advertising, or tracking tools.
GitHub Pages, which hosts the HTML game, may collect limited technical data such as IP addresses or browser type, as described in GitHubâ€™s Privacy Statement.

4. Data Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise share any personal data.

5. Children's Privacy

The Game is suitable for all ages and does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

6. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
